displayName: Archee Village, in front of Clea's house

parameters:
Clea: Wow... I can't believe this building turned out so
magnificent.

Clea (Father, Mother, I have done it. I have accomplished
what I vowed to do on that day here.)

Clea (Now I'm being called a hero, but all I did was seek
revenge on the dragon.)

Clea (I defeated the dragon, but I haven't gained anything.
I'm still left with what I lost.)

Clea: I don't know... What is the purpose of living? Should
I keep fighting...?

Carpenter Man: So you're the Dragon Slayer! Hahaha, I never
expected a girl around the same age as my daughter to be
one.

Carpenter Man: It has turned out to be a finish worthy of
an empire's hero, hasn't it?
Clea: Yes, I need to thank Lord Caron as well.

Carpenter Man: We completely rebuilt the first and second
floors, but the basement was mostly untouched, so we left it
as it was.

Carpenter Man: I'm glad the house of the empire's hero has
been built! Please live in it for as long as possible and
take good care of it!

Clea: I have finished confirming it. If I don't fulfill the
request...
Thief Nora: Ugh... my head is throbbing...

Mage Relm: Ugh... why is this happening... my head hurts...
the genius intellect... is breaking...

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, hangovers can be tough, but
eventually they turn into pleasure, you know?
Clea: Now, let's begin a new journey.

Clea (I still don't know who I am, but I want to start
walking together with my companions.)
実績 新たなる旅立ち

Village Chief Arukee: Oh, you've finally returned after a
long time!

Village Chief Arukee: You've received such a splendid
house, so at least come back and do some cleaning!

Village Chief Arukee: So are these girls your comrades in
dragon slaying?

Receptionist Piste: I am the receptionist of the
Adventurer's Guild. Nice to meet you, my name is Piste.

Village Chief Arukee: Piste-san, let's talk a little about
renting a house.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Receptionist Piste: Yes, I also received some local honey.

Receptionist Piste: Clea-chan, you have to show your face
once in a while, you know?

Receptionist Piste: The village chief was really worried
about you!

Receptionist Piste: Clea-chan, you've been on guard since
earlier, is something wrong?

Clea: I felt someone's gaze, but it suddenly disappeared
around the time I arrived at Alkay Village, so it felt
strange.

Receptionist Piste: Hmm, if it's just your imagination,
that's fine... but since this is the last one, let's finish
it quickly and go home!

Receptionist Piste: A place that is very important to me...
It's on a small hill.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

\CL Area Unlocked\c[18]\CL Fotizona Region / Hideout of the
Tomos Raiders\c[0]
